'''未爆炸弹药'''，又稱'''哑炮'''，是指在武装冲突结束后仍遗留在某一地区的各种 ( 未爆炸或被弃置的) [[爆炸性弹药|爆炸性弹药]]。其中包括[[炮弹|炮弹]]、[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]、[[地雷|地雷]]、[[迫击炮弹|迫击炮弹]]、[[火箭弹|火箭弹]]、[[导弹|导弹]]以及其他弹药。这类武器可能在被布设或遗弃数十年后[[爆炸|爆炸]]，存在致命且不稳定的危险。 <ref>{{cite news |last=Hall |first=Allan |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2497732/The-iron-harvest-Meet-soldiers-tasked-clearing-hundreds-tonnes-deadly-World-War-I-shells-mines-beneath-fields-Flanders.html |title=The iron harvest: Meet the soldiers tasked with clearing hundreds of tonnes of deadly World War I shells and mines from beneath the fields of Flanders |work=Daily Mail |date=10 November 2013 |accessdate=22 March 2014 |location=London |archive-date=2015-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526162023/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2497732/The-iron-harvest-Meet-soldiers-tasked-clearing-hundreds-tonnes-deadly-World-War-I-shells-mines-beneath-fields-Flanders.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

